The paper deals with path planning for an autonomous mobile robot, which is a common topic in the field of robotics (cs.RO). The use of swarm optimization algorithms and the proposed modification on the frequency parameter suggest that the paper may also fall under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also involves simulation experiments, which may indicate a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) as well.
